============= Passives =============
Sunlight Sensitivity: While in sunlight, the kobold has disadvantage on attack rolls, as well as on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight
Pack Tactics: The kobold has advantage on an attack roll against a ccreature if at least one of the kobold's allies is within 5 ft of the creature and the ally isn't incapacitated
